<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>fit5x Training Program - Program</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }
        main {
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .program-description {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .training-todo {
            border: 2px dashed #ccc;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            min-height: 200px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">fit5x</div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="index">Main</a>
                <a href="program">Program</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h1>fit5x Training Program</h1>
        <div class="program-description">
            <h2>About Our Program</h2>
            <p>The fit5x training program is designed to help you achieve your fitness goals through a combination of targeted exercises, proper nutrition, and expert guidance. Our program is flexible and can be tailored to your specific needs and fitness level.</p>
        </div>
        <h2>Your Training To-Do List</h2>
        <p>Below you'll find your personalized training to-do list. This list will be updated regularly to keep you on track with your fitness goals.</p>
        <div class="training-todo">
            <ul id="todo-list">
                <li>Deadlift 1x5: <%= @weight["deadlift"] %></li>
                <li>Shoulderpress 3x5: <%= @weight["shoulderpress"] %></li>
                <li>Benchpress 3x5: <%= @weight["benchpress"] %></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>